HOW TO PLAY
- Reach the flag at the end of the level.

CONTROLS
- [color=#ffac00]\[Arrow keys][/color] moves the character in any direction.
- [color=#ffac00]\[Space bar][/color] makes the character jump.

Press any key to hide the tutorial...

[color=#57ce00]YOU WIN![/color]
The game will restart in a few seconds...
